{"tid":1436519,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭爪牙已經轉打經濟民生牌吸引中立及淺藍人士, 各方必須盡快諗對策對應","createTime":"2019-08-09T10:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T10:14:25.000Z","uid":99466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29bf338162d92fb4fb2037ae19c5cd48136fed4d","tid":1436519,"uid":99466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:02:15.000Z","msg":"由8.5記者會開始到而家既記者會，林鄭政府都係專注講我地依一班抗爭者既行為係好影響香港經濟發展同埋擾民，可以夠膽死話今次大戰對經濟既影響俾沙士同金融風暴勁可見一班。<br />\n<br />\n而打經濟牌同民生牌，而以上兩者正正就係班不問政事派(HK Piggies)最想聽同最容易接受既野: 因為直接影響到自己既個人利益，賺唔到錢又發唔到圍，肯定有豬仔及既得利益者因此接受政府說詞而開始反對我地之後既示威及前線行動。<br />\n<br />\n故此我地應該要因應對家講法而諗新既方針反擊對家所打既經濟民生牌，例如: 若果林鄭及其政府肯早日正面回應我地既五大訴求，而唔係草草回應了事，示威者既抗爭行動就唔會不斷升級，香港經濟亦都唔需要承受咁大既打擊; 所以最影響香港經濟既唔係我地抗爭者而係導致今時今日咁既局面既林鄭政府等等。<br />\n<br />\n仲有其他方法既歡迎分享，各位共勉之，五大訴求，缺一不可。"},{"pid":"3af7c310b161d519d4a1a7d6eed36c21ea89a434","tid":1436519,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:14:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔係行動一律不推文回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /